    </div>
</section>

<!-- Our Story Section -->
<section class="our-story py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Our Story</h2>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>WeatherNow was founded in 2023 with a simple mission: to provide accurate, accessible, and user-friendly weather information to people around the world. What started as a small project has grown into a comprehensive weather service used by thousands of people daily.</p>
                        <p>Our team of meteorologists and developers work tirelessly to ensure that our data is not only accurate but presented in a way that's easy to understand and actionable. We believe that good weather information should be available to everyone, which is why we've built WeatherNow to be intuitive and accessible on any device.</p>
                        <p>Over the years, we've expanded our services from simple forecasts to comprehensive weather data including real-time updates, interactive maps, and detailed historical archives. As we continue to grow, our commitment to accuracy and user experience remains our top priority.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

